{"tid":819110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★iPhone 炒賣正式玩完，開放預購 30 分鐘各型號仍然大把貨存！","createTime":"2018-09-14T14:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T17:07:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"48f74742483aed79b6d809be6acd2be14da1eccb","tid":819110,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:19:48.000Z","msg":"大概由 iPhone 4 年代開始，炒賣 iPhone 已經係香港果粉或果窮每年指定動作。不過，炒賣高峰期一早已過。上年 iPhone X 作為 Apple 的 10 週年產品，原本吹風炒上港幣 10 萬，但正式出貨數日內已經好快炒完。今年？情況更加慘淡，官網開放預購長達 30 分鐘後仍然大把貨存！<br />\n<br />\n大家可以由以下截圖見到 (留意右上角電腦時間已經係下午 3:30)，所有型號均顯示有貨存可供選購。其中最貴的 iPhone Xs Max 512GB 算是最搶手的一部，只剩低 廣東道及銅鑼灣 Apple Store 可以取貨，其他型號及顏色幾乎間間都有現貨存。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2018/09/14/iphone-xs-max-pre-order/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2Fiphone-xs-max-pre-order%2F&d=D1Qal6xOCdfPlBPNdnY11Rv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=b8cb5b36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2018/09/14/iphone-xs-max-pre-order/</a>"},{"pid":"a14543df4d3ed65f4001c87ff8fad4a5de01de19","tid":819110,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf79692ecfaa8d93a729e85e0763aae61c2630c","tid":819110,"uid":5178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用家開心"},{"pid":"2dafaaf6e19a8ae850b424cc01c63bc45b132761","tid":819110,"uid":73276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:21:20.000Z","msg":"唔通真係因為強國人抵制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":